text: Cover Up is a 1949 American mystery movie directed by Alfred E. Green and starring William Bendix, Dennis O'Keefe, Art Baker, Barbara Britton, Ann E. Todd, Doro Merande, Hank Worden, Russell Armes. It was distributed by United Artists. ==Other websites== * * Category:1949 crime movies Category:1940s mystery movies Category:American crime movies Category:American mystery movies Category:Movies directed by Alfred E.
